item.title: Brühl Travel Guide (Cologne Lowland/North Rhine-Westphalia/Germany/Central Europe/Europe)
item.description: Explore the culturally significant museums and historical places, outdoor adventures, scenic views, hiking/biking routes, local food and drink scene, accommodations, transportation options and logistics, health and safety, and nearby excursions of Brühl, a charming town in Cologne Lowland, North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany.
